{"tid":2144471,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【警方譴責蘋果日報以假消息抹黑警隊】","createTime":"2020-08-07T15:41:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-08T14:48:39.000Z","uid":240362,"like":7,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"2d413f2b87bbba072ee5e38e1213d16c05304908","tid":2144471,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T15:41:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent-hkt1-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/116886101_3409231129164827_6795577299509181147_n.jpg?_nc_cat=102&amp;_nc_sid=110474&amp;_nc_ohc=uFUnMz1x__YAX_XQ8eJ&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkt1-1.xx&amp;oh=b29377fd646168c4958487b45feb201c&amp;oe=5F54D762\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkt1-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F116886101_3409231129164827_6795577299509181147_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D102%26_nc_sid%3D110474%26_nc_ohc%3DuFUnMz1x__YAX_XQ8eJ%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkt1-1.xx%26oh%3Db29377fd646168c4958487b45feb201c%26oe%3D5F54D762&h=dfa2c38f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n警方留意到蘋果日報今日﹙八月七日）有關警察「為改善公眾利益或人員利益而接受禮物」的報道，聲稱「警方以改善公眾利益之名收受捐贈禮物的金額上限由過去不多於一萬變成無上限」。對於蘋果日報涉嫌以假消息，惡意煽動讀者仇視警察，警方深表憤慨。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，警務人員在接受利益方面一向有嚴格規定，必須遵守2010年《接受利益（行政長官許可）公告》、《公務員事務規例》、公務員事務局通告、以及財務通告等規定，並須依據警隊《程序手冊》進行審批。警方不時透過警隊告示欄或其他合適的渠道提醒人員相關規定及指引。<br />\n<br />\n警方於八月六日回覆蘋果日報查詢時，已表明沒有更改有關《程序手冊》的內容，但蘋果日報仍然罔顧事實。為此警方表示遺憾和憤慨，並嚴正要求蘋果日報停止造謠，不要再以失實報道抹黑警隊"},{"pid":"7d4bac5fe19e04a79d12bbbc9b0d8fb13a96cf86","tid":2144471,"uid":133,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T15:41:51.000Z","msg":"Ok well noted."},{"pid":"e3e9c8935985fb2e1d61fd313ec160198ca0d1ad","tid":2144471,"uid":307203,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T15:42:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cPZhXgW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcPZhXgW.png&h=206c345b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a220e4224fe5124edf15fd18ddd1f6c359da40d2","tid":2144471,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e3e9c8935985fb2e1d61f